TITLE: Sweeper Filter Example
DESCRIPTION: This code shows an example usage of the sweeper filter option. It defines a filter that removes members from the cache if they haven't been accessed in the last 15 minutes and are not the bot's member.  It also sets an interval of 5 minutes for the sweeper to run.
